Source: hime
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Yao Wei (魏銘廷) <mwei@lxde.org>
Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://hime.luna.com.tw
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), libgtk2.0-dev (>= 2.20.0),
 libxtst-dev, libqt4-dev, libanthy-dev, autotools-dev
#Vcs-Git: git://git.debian.org/collab-maint/hime.git
#Vcs-Browser: http://git.debian.org/?p=collab-maint/hime.git;a=summary

Package: hime
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: im-switch | im-config, anthy
Description: GTK+ based input method for Chinese users
 HIME Input Method Editor is a input method platform, which is forked
 from the famous gcin input method.
 .
 This package contains only GTK2 immodule. For GTK3 and QT4 immodule, 
 please install hime-gtk3-immodule and hime-qt4-immodule packages.

Package: hime-dev
Section: devel
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, hime (>= ${source:Version})
Description: an GTK+ based input method platform - development files
 HIME Input Method Editor is a input method platform, which is forked
 from the famous gcin input method.
 .
 This package provides header files of hime.

Package: hime-qt4-immodule
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, hime (>= ${source:Version})
Description: QT4 input method module with hime as backend
 HIME Input Method Editor is a input method platform, which is forked
 from the famous gcin input method.
 .
 This package is the QT4 input method module (immodule) for hime.

Package: hime-gtk3-immodule
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, hime (>= ${source:Version})
Description: GTK3 input method module with hime as backend
 HIME Input Method Editor is a input method platform, which is forked
 from the famous gcin input method.
 .
 This package is the GTK3 input method module (immodule) for hime.

